{"tid":2335682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（18禁，有片慎入）黑警同人嘈跟住直接用槍爆人頭","createTime":"2020-12-22T05:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T19:25:09.000Z","uid":333488,"like":255,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"c25206d195b93aa5a2e6f2c80e0c7f95c3d82067","tid":2335682,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:17:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://crazyshit.com/cnt/medias/78934-official-the-2-biggest-scumbags-of-2020-are\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrazyshit.com%2Fcnt%2Fmedias%2F78934-official-the-2-biggest-scumbags-of-2020-are&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=97663261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://crazyshit.com/cnt/medias/78934-official-the-2-biggest-scumbags-of-2020-are</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓20日發生一起警察近距離槍殺鄰居母子事件，事發影片透過網路瘋傳，引爆民眾對於警察暴力的怒火。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n雖然行兇警員努埃茲卡（Jonel Nuezca）已經投案，但真正令人不安的是，影片中努埃茲卡的年幼女兒也在現場，甚至在案發前還大聲對被害人叫囂說「我爸是警察」，彷彿是在為父親的暴行助陣。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n綜合外媒報導，46歲資深警員努埃茲卡老家住在丹轆省（Tarlac）帕尼基（Paniqui），但被分派在大馬尼拉都會區的帕拉納克市（Paranaque City）警察局工作。案發當天，努埃茲卡返鄉休假，卻與鄰居家人發生爭執。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n據稱，努埃茲卡本來就與鄰居葛瑞格里歐（Gregorio）一家人素有產權糾紛，而他返鄉休假時，又發現有不明人士施放自製爆竹，因此在未穿著警察制服的情況下，攜帶手槍前去理論，並打算在沒有證據的情況下逮捕25歲鄰居法蘭克（Frank Gregorio）。法蘭克的母親、52歲的桑雅（Sonya Gregorio ）則上前攔阻。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在流傳影片中，可以看見努埃茲卡惡狠狠地瞪著法蘭克，而努埃茲卡的女兒則在旁激動大喊「我爸是警察」。與此同時，護子心切的桑雅緊緊抱著兒子，想避免兩人進一步衝突，並大喊，「我才不在乎你是不是警察」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n聽到這番話後，狂怒的努埃茲卡高喊「你要我現在就宰了你們嗎？」。下一秒，他竟舉起手槍射擊桑雅頭部，又對法蘭克連開兩槍，最後再對已經倒地的桑雅補上一槍，當場將2人殺害。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母天下烏鴉一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cbc54ac96bfc9f4a996e75ea634c6868dc64bb","tid":2335682,"uid":7369,"like":109,"dislike":4,"score":105,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"菲律賓不嬲都係咁架啦"},{"pid":"7a3c0420f0eb595ee6e3049b832fc7929f8b7012","tid":2335682,"uid":50660,"like":2,"dislike":46,"score":-44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"第二果個殺自己老母？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac841debfc3f9150b1bb08d0783a27c60f2ed7e0","tid":2335682,"uid":341613,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"咁樣殺左兩個生命"},{"pid":"ad5f75e9036b338cbcccf747173f90af976fdd8d","tid":2335682,"uid":165749,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"不意外，但意外俾人影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c763073d84164f27af82ed4da9abdb2c87b7187","tid":2335682,"uid":47658,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推上國際戰線"},{"pid":"44ee0311f195ac1fecae52fbfe8b46ca3e975b9c","tid":2335682,"uid":45255,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"港警: 我鍾意開槍打邊個打邊個，再嘈連我個處長都打埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645d723195e8b1eb6a80962e28937e32bf40b32a","tid":2335682,"uid":10881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:28:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c17d5b0083022dc23cbeec0fda05e07a22af9750","tid":2335682,"uid":14422,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"原來菲律賓都好過香港"},{"pid":"9130a715fcb4523649dea9eb0f3ed7ea0edc458b","tid":2335682,"uid":217049,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"藍絲快啲移民過去<br />\n佢哋啲理想國度<br />\n<br />\n成班畜牲"},{"pid":"13d78644fc1ef8b0ba970ba44b7aebfd624cca87","tid":2335682,"uid":288304,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:31:10.000Z","msg":"入面D片唔錯"},{"pid":"b9487613831cc7d566924594eda9589289edf91b","tid":2335682,"uid":34577,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"個白衫女仔好似唔驚噉 <img src=\"/assets/face