,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"電光火石之間可以做任何嘢。"},{"pid":"2ed75843a9a7b43da862d560e996698612c32bed","tid":2335682,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"成班生蕃,CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805d8549d8938a881bfda5f389634bc012a5f365","tid":2335682,"uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:01:38.000Z","msg":"呢個網我睇咗好耐 <a href=\"http://crazyshit.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcrazyshit.com&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=4ac956f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">crazyshit.com</a><br />\n啲人成日upload 咸嘢就冇睇<br />\n<br />\n奶把刀個下好笑 扮哂嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8070d6adbd28f046a52644079b35cca49497f2e7","tid":2335682,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"呢個咩野網來架 未聽過 唔敢㩒 係咪毒link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce946af3d059e5aad9885c6a86e6c46d7211786","tid":2335682,"uid":154429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"菲律賓警察真係有槍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d79248a5a2e3ccc9d9b3f96b1825394a26849ea","tid":2335682,"uid":353621,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c763073d84164f27af82ed4da9abdb2c87b7187","tid":2335682,"uid":47658,"like":3,"dislike":24,"score":-21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推上國際戰線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>一早blocked</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"838b2c993b9ef0a17ae0